<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Easy Travel BD</h1>
    <p>Easy Travel BD is a comprehensive travel management platform designed to make traveling across Bangladesh convenient and enjoyable. From booking bus tickets to finding the best hotels, tour guides, and travel agencies, our platform provides a seamless experience for travelers. Additionally, Easy Travel BD enables users to explore tourist spots, read blogs, and share their travel experiences.</p>
