    <h2>Features</h2>
    <h3>Home Page</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Navbar with buttons for Packages, Buy Bus Ticket, Book Hotel, Book Guide, Explore Spots in Bangladesh</li>
        <li>Hero Section showcasing major services: Bus Ticketing, Hotel Booking, Travel Agency, Packages</li>
        <li>Body with attractive cards showcasing travel packages and details of popular tourist spots in Bangladesh</li>
        <li>Footer with quick links and contact details</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Buy Ticket Page</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Ticket Search with input fields for From, To, and Date, and a search button to show available buses</li>
        <li>Bus Selection with a list of available buses and seat selection option</li>
        <li>Payment System (if applicable)</li>
        <li>Ticket Download to generate and download a ticket copy</li>
        <li>Additional Suggestion to display nearby hotels at the destination area</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Tour Booking Page</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>List of hotels with photos, descriptions, and prices</li>
        <li>Detailed information and booking options for selected hotels</li>
        <li>Booking documents as a printable copy</li>
        <li>Location Selector to filter hotels by location</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Travel Agency Page</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>List of trusted travel agencies with detailed information and hiring options</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Blog Page</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Admin (and optionally users) can post blogs about tourist spots, travel tips, experiences, and recommendations</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Admin Page</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Manage platform data: Add or remove buses, hotels, travel agencies</li>
        <li>Post about tourist spots</li>
        <li>Manage user accounts</li>
        <li>View and respond to user feedback</li>
        <li>Monitor platform analytics</li>
        <li>Assign roles to users</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Frontend: React, Next.js framework</li>
        <li>Backend: ASP.Net Core</li>
        <li>Database: MS SQL Server</li>
        <li>Authentication</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Vision</h2>
    <p>Easy Travel BD aims to revolutionize the travel experience in Bangladesh by offering a one-stop platform for all travel needs. Whether you're a solo traveler, a family, or a tour group, our application is designed to make your journey smooth, secure, and memorable.</p>

